-- Ergo Plans to Expand Property, Casualty Insurance, Welt Reports
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-02-19T11:13:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-19/ergo-plans-to-expand-property-casualty-insurance-welt-reports.html
Ergo Versicherungsgruppe, the
primary insurer of Munich Re, plans to expand its property and
casualty-insurance business, Welt am Sonntag reported, citing an
interview with Chief Executive Officer Torsten Oletzky.  Oletzky said he is “optimistic” for 2012, the German
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
